\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 eztoc-toggle-hide-by-default' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-a-laboratory-scientist\/#Steps_to_become_a_Lab-Scientist\" title=\"Steps to become a Lab-Scientist\">Steps to become a Lab-Scientist<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-a-laboratory-scientist\/#Medical_Laboratory_Technologist\" title=\"Medical Laboratory Technologist\">Medical Laboratory Technologist<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-a-laboratory-scientist\/#Estimated_SalaryHow_to_Become_a_Laboratory_Scientist\" title=\"Estimated Salary\/How to Become a Laboratory Scientist\">Estimated Salary\/How to Become a Laboratory Scientist<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-a-laboratory-scientist\/#Basic_Skill_Required_How_to_Become_a_Laboratory_Scientist\" title=\"Basic Skill Required\/ How to Become a Laboratory Scientist\">Basic Skill Required\/ How to Become a Laboratory Scientist<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-a-laboratory-scientist\/#Jobs_in_Med_Laboratory\" title=\"Jobs in Med Laboratory\">Jobs in Med Laboratory<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-a-laboratory-scientist\/#Education_needed_in_Laboratory\" title=\"Education needed in Laboratory\">Education needed in Laboratory<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-a-laboratory-scientist\/#Subject_in_Laboratory\" title=\"Subject in Laboratory\">Subject in Laboratory<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-a-laboratory-scientist\/#Job_in_crime_MLT_How_to_Become_a_Laboratory_Scientist\" title=\"Job in crime MLT\/ How to Become a Laboratory Scientist\">Job in crime MLT\/ How to Become a Laboratory Scientist<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: center;\"><strong>Becoming a Lab-Scientist requires variety of skills and as well education qualification to enable you being employ and as well being expose to the basic ideas. learn more on how to become an MLT below.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-2161 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/service-203-118-784167346-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"How to Become a Med Lab-scientist\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><strong>Contents<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82589834\">Steps to become a Lab-Scientist<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82589835\">Medical Laboratory Technologist<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82589836\">Estimated Salary<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82589837\">Basic Skill Required<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82589838\">Jobs in Med Laboratory<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82589839\">Education needed in Laboratory<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82589840\">Subject in Laboratory<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82589841\">Job in crime MLT<\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"steps-to-become-a-lab-scientist\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Steps_to_become_a_Lab-Scientist\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82589834\"><\/a>Steps to become a Lab-Scientist<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong><em>To become a MLT you must first:<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Find entry level work<\/li>\n<li>Earn at least ASCP certification<\/li>\n<li>Get a high school diploma<\/li>\n<li>Gain a clinical experience<\/li>\n<li>Have a bachelor\u2019s degree.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Read Also&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/medical-scholarships\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Medical Scholarships in UK, Europe, Australia<\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"medical-laboratory-technologist\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Medical_Laboratory_Technologist\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82589835\"><\/a>Medical Laboratory Technologist<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>It is a regulated profession in all Canada provinces except for British Columbia Prince Edward Island (PEI), and the Territories.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"estimated-salary-how-to-become-a-laboratory-scientist\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Estimated_SalaryHow_to_Become_a_Laboratory_Scientist\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82589836\"><\/a>Estimated Salary\/How to Become a Laboratory Scientist<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>The average salary of MLT in Canada is $45,495 per year or $23.33 per hour<\/li>\n<li>Entry level positions start at $34,938 per year and $60,408 per year.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"basic-skill-required-how-to-become-a-laboratory-scientist\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Basic_Skill_Required_How_to_Become_a_Laboratory_Scientist\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82589837\"><\/a>Basic Skill Required\/ How to Become a Laboratory Scientist<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Knowledge of chemistry including the safe use and disposal of chemicals.<\/li>\n<li>Knowledge of biology.<\/li>\n<li>The ability to work well with your hands.<\/li>\n<li>To be thorough and pay attention to detail.<\/li>\n<li>The ability to use your initiative.<\/li>\n<li>The ability to work well with others.<\/li>\n<li>Administration skills.<\/li>\n<li>Maths knowledge.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"jobs-in-med-laboratory\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Jobs_in_Med_Laboratory\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82589838\"><\/a>Jobs in Med Laboratory<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>There are many types of laboratory professionals, including<\/strong><strong>:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Medical Laboratory Scientists.<\/li>\n<li>Medical Laboratory Technicians.<\/li>\n<li>Cytotechnologist<\/li>\n<li>Histotechnologist<\/li>\n<li>Phlebotomist<\/li>\n<li>Molecular Biologists.<\/li>\n<li>Pathologists&#8217; Assistants.<\/li>\n<li>Clinical Chemists.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"education-needed-in-laboratory\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Education_needed_in_Laboratory\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82589839\"><\/a>Education needed in Laboratory<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Lab technicians need at minimum a high school diploma or equivalent to work. Most companies prefer at least an Associate&#8217;s Degree in Laboratory Science or related major. It can be helpful to earn a degree from an institution accredited by the National Accrediting Agency for Clinical Laboratory Sciences.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"subject-in-laboratory\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Subject_in_Laboratory\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82589840\"><\/a>Subject in Laboratory<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Health Education and Health Communication.<\/li>\n<li>Human Anatomy.<\/li>\n<li>Human Physiology.<\/li>\n<li>PC Software Lab.<\/li>\n<li>Bio-Medical Waste Management.<\/li>\n<li>Communication Lab.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"job-in-crime-mlt-how-to-become-a-laboratory-scientist\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Job_in_crime_MLT_How_to_Become_a_Laboratory_Scientist\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82589841\"><\/a>Job in crime MLT\/ How to Become a Laboratory Scientist<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong><em>Jobs directly related to your degree include:<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Analytical chemist.<\/li>\n<li>Biomedical scientist.<\/li>\n<li>Crime scene investigator.<\/li>\n<li>Detective<\/li>\n<li>Forensic scientist.<\/li>\n<li>Scientific laboratory technician.<\/li>\n<li>Toxicologist<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><em><strong>See also &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; <\/strong><\/em><a title=\"How to Become a Dermatologist in Canada\" href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-a-dermatologist\/\" rel=\"bookmark nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><em><strong>How to Become a Dermatologist in Canada<\/strong><\/em><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"How to Become a Laboratory Scientist- scientist, Jobs in Med Laboratory, Subject in Laboratory, basic Skills required, estimated&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":2165,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[14],"tags":[728],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2164"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2164"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2164\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":19204,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2164\/revisions\/19204"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2164"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2164"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2164"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","